&lt;h2 id="2disable-if-possible-the-kernel-mode-setting-ksm-of-the-graphics-card-we-add-the-following-line-in-the-group-configuration"&gt;2.Disable if possible the Kernel Mode Setting (KSM) of the graphics card. We add the following line in the group configuration:&lt;/h2&gt;
